End-to-End Flow

1. Developer React app mein changes karta hai
         ↓
2. Code push → Azure Repos (main branch)
         ↓
3. CI Pipeline trigger hoti hai
   ├─ Docker image build (multi-stage)
   ├─ Image test hoti hai
   └─ Image ACR mein push hoti hai
         ↓
4. CD Pipeline trigger hoti hai
   └─ ACI pe purana container replace hota hai
         ↓
5. User browser se new version access karta hai
   URL: http://<<aci-ip-address>

   Outro
